query:
INSERT INTO pocket_article_authors (
                pocket_article_id, 
                author_id, 
                name, 
                url
            )
            VALUES (
                $1,
                $2,
                $3,
                $4
            )
            ON CONFLICT (
                pocket_article_id, 
                author_id
            ) 
            DO UPDATE
            SET
            name = EXCLUDED.name, 
            url = EXCLUDED.url
            RETURNING id
